You might think finding six double-yolk eggs in one box is about as likely as discovering a unicorn munching through a field of four-leaf clovers.

However, Marks & Spencer has cut the odds to the point where it is a certainty.

The chain is launching boxes of six extra-large eggs with every one guaranteed to have two golden, gooey yolks – a product M&S says is ‘perfect for people who think the yolk is the best bit’.

